Info-Retrieval-Tasks:
	- If the task is to retrieve a piece of information
	- based on previous milestones, if the tester reaches a certain point, he needs to answer a quiz based on the information to retrieve
	- Algorithm:
	
	Inputs:
		- Milestone X: The milestone before the actual retrieval of the information takes place
		- Event current: Current activity
	Output: 
	IF( current matches X) {
		Load Quiz;
		Load Quiz-Button;
	}
	
	IF(QuizIsAnsweredCorrectly) {
		Finish Task;
	}
	
	Data-Requirements:
		- Type-Info for Task
		- Quiz-Content
	Functional-Requirements:
		- info-retrieval mode in view layer
		- detection in view layer, whether milestone x has been reached